                and overall increased life satisfaction.</p>
        </div>



        <div id="features" class="container">
            <p>Our free platform enables you to: </p>
            <ul>
                <div>
                    <li style='font-size:1.2rem;'>&#128200; Track your mood</li>
                    <img src="" alt="">
                </div>


                <div>
                    <li style='font-size:1.2rem;'>&#128269;Uncover patterns</li>
                    <img src="" alt="">
                </div>


                <div>
                    <li style='font-size:1.2rem;'>&#128161;Gain actionable insights</li>
                    <img src="" alt="">
                </div>


            </ul>

        </div>

        <div id="closing-pitch" class="container">

            <p>Transform your life, one snapshot at a time!</p>
            <p>Sign up today and start your journey to a happier, more aware you.</p>

            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" id="signup-btn" onclick="location.href='./register'">
                Get Started
            </button>

            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary" id="login-btn" onclick="location.href='./login'">
                Log In
            </button>

        </div>


    </main>

    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"
        integrity="sha384-C6RzsynM9kWDrMNeT87bh95OGNyZPhcTNXj1NW7RuBCsyN/o0jlpcV8Qyq46cDfL"
